data.description: 15K Seller Concessions with full price offer! New Roof completed on 2/12/2024. Stainless steel appliances included! Granite counters in the kitchen with an island and pantry. Vaulted ceilings. Tile floors throughout, carpet in all the bedrooms. Primary bedroom has a walk in closet  with a full bathroom and double sinks. Washer and dryer included. Large covered patio with french doors. Extended height block fence in the backyard. Green belt located across the street with a playground.
